  "name": "Unyielding Knight",
  "ownership": {
    "default": 0
  },
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Raising your shield, you call out for aid from the champions of the gods. You choose an unoccupied point or willing creature within range, conjuring a spectral knight in that space. The knight is Medium, can't take actions or reactions, and is immune to all damage. Creatures of your choice can pass freely through the knight's space and end their turns there, but the knight is impassable for others. A creature in the knight's space has three-quarters cover against all attacks directed at them.</p><p>As a bonus action, you can move any knights summoned by this spell up to 10 feet.</p><p><strong><em>At Higher Levels:</em></strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th level or higher, you summon one additional knight for each slot level above 3rd.</p>",
